channel.title: INDIR3CT- Ice cream [Trap] Fixed virtual ice cream cone!
channel.description:
Hey everyone! In October I posted this trap song "Ice Cream" , https://disco.auxy.co/t/ice-cream-by-indir3ct-trap/3447?u=indir3ct
It said click like for a virtual ice cream cone, but...It didn't actually work :frowning: Now I got it fixed! Either go to the soundcloud page, and access the link there to get your ice cream cone or sundae , or just click the bottom link on this thread. https://soundcloud.com/indir3ct/ice-cream
http://www.cybercones.com/page2.htm
(P.S.) I don't mean to repost this track or spam it :P just want to share the Ice Cream
